room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: Had a blast. Never would have expected it but I did. We did the Museum Heist this time and wouldn't mind going back to try another.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: Had a great time with the Museum Heist. Will was a great game master making the whole experience a lot of fun. Went for a birthday get together among friends with a successful escape. We'll have to come back again

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: I went for the first time a couple of days ago and had a blast. We broke out within the last 20 seconds and our game master, Sara, was amazing also. Definitely having a good team that works together makes a big difference. We did Museum Heist. Definitely will be back.

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: We had so much fun last night! I highly recommend getting friends together and have a great time! We did Museum Heist! Abby was a great game master!! I will definitely be going back!!

room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Dayton in Dayton
review: My work team had a great time at Breakout Dayton! Will was our game master and was fantastic at guiding us through our heist (without officially giving us clues). Definitely head here with your team, family, or friends - it's lots of fun!
